reviewText: Very old video of a guy dribbling a soccerball like a basketball
Ok but I was expecting more
This has been a fun addition to my weekly workouts, im less uncoordinated at it each week.
Love soccerobics!  Outstanding way for your kids to improve their soccer skills!

This video is definitely worth checking out.  It's a little dated (looks like from the 80's, maybe early 90's), but with all the drills and exercise, I don't see how you can't benefit from this to one degree or another.

The ball handling exercises on the front of the tape remind me of basketball exercises, but may be good for goalkeepers.  The ball touch exercises on the rest of the tape can be done in a small area in front of  the TV.
